 them to refrain from bullying.\\\"\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 779, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The victories of Khelif and fellow boxer Lin Yu-ting of Taiwan in the ring in Paris have become one of the biggest stories of the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 923, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 822, \"end\": 833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 837, \"end\": 843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9999999987276169, \"rank\": 6.502094571633952e-10, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 859, \"end\": 864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.0364407565990155e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The victories\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 794}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 855}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest stories\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 903}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both women have clinched their first Olympic medals even as they have faced online abuse based on unsubstantiated claims about their gender, drawing them into a wider divide over changing attitudes toward gender identity and regulations in sports.\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 1171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Both women\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"their first Olympic medals\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"online abuse\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1012}, {\"ngram\": \"unsubstantiated claims\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"their gender\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"a wider divide\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"attitudes\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1121}, {\"ngram\": \"gender identity\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1144}, {\"ngram\": \"regulations\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1160}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old Khelif acknowledged the pressure and pain of enduring this ordeal while competing far from home in the most important event of her athletic career.\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 25-year-old Khelif\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"this ordeal\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"the most important event\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1312}, {\"ngram\": \"her athletic career\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am in contact with my family two days a week.\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1386, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"contact\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope that they were not affected deeply,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are worried about me.\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"God willing, this crisis will culminate in a gold medal, and that would be the best response.\\\"\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1563, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this crisis\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"the best response\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vitriol stems from claims by the International Boxing Association, which has been permanently banned from the Olympics, that both Khelif and Lin failed unspecified eligibility tests for the women's competition at last year's world championships.\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1814, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1602, \"end\": 1634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.235508562698947e-32, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The vitriol\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"claims\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1594}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"both Khelif\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"unspecified eligibility tests\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1750}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's competition\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's world championships\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1813}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif declined to answer when asked whether she had undergone tests other than doping tests, saying she did not want to talk about it.\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1822}, {\"ngram\": \"undergone tests\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"doping tests\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She expressed gratitude to the International Olympic Committee and its president, Thomas Bach, for standing resolutely behind her while the banned former governing body of Olympic boxing stoked a furor around her participation in Paris.\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 2189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1984, \"end\": 2015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2035, \"end\": 2046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 2183, \"end\": 2188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.0364407565990155e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gratitude\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"its president\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2033}, {\"ngram\": \"the banned former governing body\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2121}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic boxing\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2139}, {\"ngram\": \"a furor\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"her participation\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know that the Olympic Committee has done me justice, and I am happy with this remedy because it shows the truth,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Committee\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2225}, {\"ngram\": \"justice\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"this remedy\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"the truth\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also has seen massive support at her bouts, drawing cheers when she enters the arena and crowds waving Algerian flags chanting her first name.\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2426, \"end\": 2434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999992799555776, \"rank\": 5.388636516887886e-07, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"massive support\", \"from\": 2337, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"her bouts\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2365}, {\"ngram\": \"cheers\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2407}, {\"ngram\": \"crowds\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2418}, {\"ngram\": \"her first name\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She will fight again Tuesday in the women's 66-kilogram semifinals at Roland Garros.\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2550, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the women's 66-kilogram semifinals\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2532}, {\"ngram\": \"Roland Garros\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif repeatedly made clear she will not allow chatter or accusations to deter her from attempting to claim Algeria's first Olympic gold medal in women's boxing.\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2661, \"end\": 2668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999999587948887, \"rank\": 2.3245405926687533e-08, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2558}, {\"ngram\": \"chatter\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"accusations\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"women's boxing\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not care about anyone's opinion,\\\" Khelif said a day after beating Anna Luca Hamori of Hungary.\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2788, \"end\": 2792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\", \"score\": 0.9969898961674867, \"rank\": 0.0030187684936047727, \"text\": \"Anna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\"}, {\"begin\": 2808, \"end\": 2815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.7283424309727655, \"rank\": 0.2471885197784326, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone's opinion\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2753}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I came here for a medal, and to compete for a medal.\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2870, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2841}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will certainly be competing to improve (and) be better, and God willing, I will improve, like every other athlete.\\\"\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2936}, {\"ngram\": \"every other athlete\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although she is aware of the worldwide discussion about her, Khelif said she has been somewhat removed.\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 3093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the worldwide discussion\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3039}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 3051, \"to\": 3057}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Honestly, I do not follow social media,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3146, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a mental health team that does not let us follow social media, especially in the Olympic Games, whether me or other athletes.\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mental health team\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3177}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3198}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3218}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3251}, {\"ngram\": \"whether me\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3263}, {\"ngram\": \"other athletes\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am here to compete and get a good result.\\\"\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good result\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif started her Olympic run last Thursday with a victory over Angela Carini of Italy, who abandoned the bout after just 46 seconds.\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3394, \"end\": 3407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 3411, \"end\": 3416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7976042124717735, \"rank\": 0.24737130847050884, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3335}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic run\", \"from\": 3344, \"to\": 3359}, {\"ngram\": \"a victory\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3388}, {\"ngram\": \"the bout\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3440}, {\"ngram\": \"just 46 seconds\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini later said she regretted her decision and wished to apologize to Khelif.\", \"from\": 3464, \"to\": 3543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3464, \"end\": 3470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9982417297590197, \"rank\": 0.0017613672006174836, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her decision\", \"from\": 3496, \"to\": 3508}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That unusual ending raised the chatter around Khelif into a roar, drawing comments from the likes of former U.S. President Donald Trump, \\\"Harry Potter\\\" writer J.K. Rowling and others falsely claiming Khelif was a man or transgender.\", \"from\": 3545, \"to\": 3777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3668, \"end\": 3680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999952124199, \"rank\": 4.787401909259538e-09, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 3683, \"end\": 3695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"score\": 0.9999999991819095, \"rank\": 8.001233262932761e-10, \"text\": \"Harry Potter\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\"}, {\"begin\": 3704, \"end\": 3708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.794698568890132e-29, \"text\": \"J.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That unusual ending\